{"General": {"Code": "80016", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited", "Exchange": "HK", "CurrencyCode": "HKD", "CurrencyName": "Hong Kong Dollar", "CurrencySymbol": "HK$", "CountryName": "Hong Kong", "CountryISO": "HK", "OpenFigi": "BBG01GXJND56", "ISIN": null, "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": null, "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "June", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "", "Industry": "", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "Description": "Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited, an investment holding company, develops and invests in properties for sale and rent in Hong Kong, Mainland China, and internationally. It develops, sells, and leases properties, including residential estates, offices, shopping malls, and hotels and serviced suites. The company also provides property management services; construction-related services, including landscaping, electrical and mechanical installation, production and installation of wooden doors, and construction plant and machinery leasing; and insurance products to individuals and businesses comprising householder's comprehensive, fire, employees' compensation, travel, personal accident, motor vehicles, contractors' all risks, third party liability, and property all risks. In addition, it offers public bus, car parks, toll roads, and retail department stores services; data centre, facilities management, and value-added services; general insurance; and airport freight forwarding services. Further, the company provides insurance and mortgage services; mobile telephone, data centres, and IT infrastructure services; and transport infrastructure operation and management, port, and air transport and logistic services, as well as Internet of Things (IoT) solutions. Additionally, it offers mobile telephone system operation services; asset and project management services; loan financing; fire prevention and mechanical engineering services; architectural and engineering services; property and facility management services; business aviation centre services; real estate and general agency services; and secretarial services, as well as manufactures and sells ready mixed and precast concrete. The company also engages in the hotel operation business. The company was formerly known as Sun Hung Kai (Holdings) Limited and changed its name to Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited in March 1973. Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.", "Address": "Sun Hung Kai Centre, Wan Chai, Hong Kong", "AddressData": {"Street": "Sun Hung Kai Centre", "City": "Wan Chai", "Country": "Hong Kong"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Ping-Luen  Kwok Hon DBA, Hon LLD, J.P., M.A., M.B.A., MA (Cantab)", "Title": "Executive Chairman & MD", "YearBorn": "1953"}, "1": {"Name": "Mr. Chi-Ho  Tung Aut, B.A., BA(AS)Hons, BArch, HKIA, Reg Architect", "Title": "Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1959"}, "2": {"Name": "Mr. Ting  Lui B.B.A.", "Title": "Deputy MD & Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1955"}, "3": {"Name": "Mr. Chik-wing  Wong FHKIS, J.P., M.Sc., MSc(IRE), RPS (BS)", "Title": "Deputy MD & Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1956"}, "4": {"Name": "Mr. Kai-fai  Kwok B.Sc., M.B.A.", "Title": "Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1983"}, "5": {"Name": "Mr. Yuk-Lun  Fung B.A., Ph.D.", "Title": "Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1968"}, "6": {"Name": "Mr. Kai-Wang  Kwok B.Sc., J.P., M.B.A.", "Title": "Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1987"}, "7": {"Name": "Mr. Hong-Ki  Chan B.Sc., MRICS", "Title": "Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1965"}, "8": {"Name": "Mr. Ching-Kam  Li C.P.A., FCCA", "Title": "Chief Accountant", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "9": {"Name": "Mr. Thomas MK  Chan", "Title": "Head of Investor Relations", "YearBorn": "NA"}}, "Phone": "852 2827 8111", "WebURL": "https://www.shkp.com", "LogoURL": "", "FullTimeEmployees": 38000, "UpdatedAt": "2026-03-19"}, "Highlights